title: Exchange Hybrid: What, How and Why?  All The Latest Things You Need To Know About Connecting Exchange to the Cloud
sortTitle: exchange hybrid: what, how and why?  all the latest things you need to know about connecting exchange to the cloud
description: Microsoft Exchange hybrid agent was released to GA removing a major blocker for customers who wanted to use a lightweight configuration for hybrid scenarios in their environments. This session offers best practices for using the hybrid configuration to move on-premises Exchange mailboxes to the cloud and presents advanced scenarios with multiple Exchanges forests, AD tenants and how to set them up in consolidated cloud environments.
